{"tid":2155602,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"獲釋後Twitter直播  黎智英：手銬不能侮辱我","createTime":"2020-08-14T01:49:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T01:51:02.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"135d0bd2591b51f7443699838d9ddc718003ba2f","tid":2155602,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T01:49:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200814/6QANPKUMMFGPJNTSC6UTNPSK64/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200814%2F6QANPKUMMFGPJNTSC6UTNPSK64%2F&d=Bi55TGPCxKeiDoZ%2FBZgBR29V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=46b80633\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200814%2F6QANPKUMMFGPJNTSC6UTNPSK64%2F&h=03a93109\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200814/6QANPKUMMFGPJNTSC6UTNPSK64/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n獲釋後Twitter直播 <br />\n黎智英：手銬不能侮辱我<br />\n<br />\n【瘋狂搜捕】<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：彭定康籲向國際法院狀告中共<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】當警察把他鎖上手銬，他處之泰然未視屈辱；困在警署羈留室席地而睡，他未言後悔，更欣然接受；但當支持者誠摯表示支持，他終被觸動。壹傳媒創辦人黎智英被指違反港版國安法被捕後獲保釋，昨早在Twitter如常「經營國際線」，他分享時強調，即使被扣上手銬，他從沒有一刻「覺得自己很慘，或覺得自己被屈辱」，但當海外讀者表達支持說：「你很了不起&hellip;&hellip;我很尊敬你」，黎智英回應「多謝」一刻，再難掩激動，終感觸落淚。<br />\n<br />\n黎智英在Twitter直播時，親述被捕和扣查的感受，又與網民交流。《南華早報》前總編輯Mark Clifford及美國傳統基金會艾里森外。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：金融時報：港新聞自由已死<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/IE7TXU3GcgW7ct_pdicO_zcGiRA=/2658x1772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SENDTKTHVZHYNGX74BLFNJYEGI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FIE7TXU3GcgW7ct_pdicO_zcGiRA%3D%2F2658x1772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSENDTKTHVZHYNGX74BLFNJYEGI.jpg&h=ff8cacfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■黎智英昨早如常在Twitter直播並親述被捕感受，在獲得大量支持者為自己打氣後，終難掩感觸心情落下淚來。馬泉崇攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n指中共不明白言論自由是港基石<br />\n<br />\n黎智英憶述，當天早上在家運動後讀報，突有15至20名警員上門拉人，他要求洗澡後才離開，警員卻要他打開浴室門，在監視下洗澡。雖然他早前亦曾因參與六四悼念集會而被捕，但今次是首度被扣上手銬，不過黎智英直言：「沒有一刻，我的手在手銬之下時，覺得自己很慘，或覺得自己被屈辱，我完全沒有這個感覺」，並指離開警署時，看到很多人到場支持，感到非常感激。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n嘉賓之一的Mark Clifford指，即使很多香港人已發聲，但中方拒絕與人民談。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n獲美國支持者打氣感觸落淚<br />\n<br />\n及至問答環節，身處美國的網民Nicole與黎智英對談，表示沒有問題提出，「我只想說你很了不起&hellip;&hellip;我很尊敬你。」Nicole又透露將會參與紐約集會支持黎智英。黎回應時說了一句「多謝」後，再難掩感觸心情並落下淚來。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n直播期間，大量讀者留言向黎打氣及表達支持，黎智英回應時再度硬咽表示多。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/m9841sCxM8lPAZa-AtQBs0rwix4=/1377x827/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JPGVESTBGVEGNKPOMMSVVPTOJQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fm9841sCxM8lPAZa-AtQBs0rwix4%3D%2F1377x827%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJPGVESTBGVEGNKPOMMSVVPTOJQ.jpg&h=231e5ecf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■身處美國的Nicole昨於直播問答環節中為黎智英打氣，敬佩黎為爭取民主自由押上人生。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/0DGiDg4L3FOJvO1AuiRKFXc5q38=/1704x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MU3CIBCV4VFLZEUZ7FCJEYYMMA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F0DGiDg4L3FOJvO1AuiRKFXc5q38%3D%2F1704x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMU3CIBCV4VFLZEUZ7FCJEYYMMA.jpg&h=207e9bd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■黎智英早前曾因參與六四集會被捕，惟本周一的一次卻是首度被鎖上手銬。"},{"pid":"0c340f6155b3cd4edb4f0d928cffb3f101e40d5a","tid":2155602,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T01:51:02.000Z","msg":"聯署支持封殺微信同TikTok<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/we-people-support-ban-wechat-and-tiktok\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fwe-people-support-ban-wechat-and-tiktok&d=Bi55TGPCxKeiDoZ%2FBZgBR29V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=8e66df3b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/we-people-support-ban-wechat-and-tiktok</a>"}]}